OOC: She doesn't have a "face" per se in jet form - and that's a damn 
good shot, considering she's still at a respectable altitude and 
moving fast.  I'll let the gist go by, though ...

Empath::

The treacherous femme banks as she is fired on, her enhanced 
perception telling her the shot would miss anyway but old reflexes 
getting the better of her for a moment.  <The time for talk is past, 
avian,> she transmits in response.  <The time for my revenge is NOW!>

...

If she had broken the connection any harder, it would have screamed.
